         Use of RSA Keys with SHA-256 and SHA-512 in the Secure Shell
         (SSH) Protocol
       RFC 8446:
         The Transport Layer Security (TLS) Protocol Version 1.3";
  }

  identity rsassa-pkcs1-sha384 {
